How to use this document
When you receive an internal (RFC1918) IP address to investigate:
Match the IP against the subnet ranges below to identify the network segment
If the IP matches a specific host entry, return that host's identity and role
Use the threat context notes to frame your analysis appropriately
Cross-reference observer.name (sensor ID) with the sensor coverage section

