User subnet profile
All Div1 user subnets (192.168.110–170.x) share this profile:
Mix: 6 × Windows 7, 1 × non-Microsoft Windows 7, 1 × Windows XP, 1 × Windows Vista, 1 × Linux
Patch level: varied — some systems intentionally unsupported and unpatched
Linux kernel: all Linux hosts ≤ 3.13 (intentionally vulnerable)
Scale: 10 users per subnet, .1 = gateway, .2-.10 = users typically
High-value subnets: Intel (161-163), Finance/HQ (111), Medical (166)

