SCOM port reference
Port 5723 (TCP) is exclusively used by Microsoft System Center Operations Manager (SCOM). Legitimate sources/destinations: 10.0.40.52, 10.0.40.53, 10.0.40.54 only. Any 5723/5724 traffic NOT involving these three IPs is anomalous and indicates either attacker abuse or a rogue SCOM agent.

